            Click here to view and download a copy or do so below!
        </a>
        <div>
            <object class="hidden-xs hidden-sm" data="~/Content/Files/Michael Krimm  IT Resume.pdf" type="application/pdf" width="100%" height="800px" internalinstanceid="13" style="padding-top: 20px; padding-bottom: 5px;">
